INTRODUCTION: GLOBAL NEURODIVERSITY IS NOT A DEFICIT
The Node
In this document, we use the term Node. Every neurodivergent person is a unique, valuable point in a global networkâ€”a nervous system, a society, a community. A node receives and sends signals, connects across cultures, and holds strength in authenticity and lived experience. We are all nodes in the network.
